## 2. Entity Relationships

* **SemesterProfile to Subject**: One-to-Many. A semester has many subjects. Deleting a semester deletes its subjects.
* **SemesterProfile to TimetableSlot**: One-to-Many. A semester has a weekly timetable. Deleting a semester deletes its timetable slots.
* **SemesterProfile to SemesterEvent**: One-to-Many. A semester contains many events. Deleting a semester deletes its events.
* **Subject to TimetableSlot**: One-to-Many. A subject is taught in multiple time slots per week. Deleting a subject removes its timetable occurrences.
* **EventTypeDefinition to SemesterEvent**: One-to-Many. Many events can use the same event type preset. (No cascade delete allowed on system presets).

