## 7. Database Migration Strategy

* **Initialization**: SQLite will be used (`app.db`).
* **Alembic**: Alembic will be configured and initialized in the `backend/alembic/` directory.
* **Migrations**: We will generate an initial migration script (`alembic revision --autogenerate -m "init_schema"`) which captures all M1 models.
* **Future Changes**: Any future schema tweaks will use standard Alembic workflow (`alembic revision` -> `alembic upgrade head`), keeping the database state strictly version-controlled.

